(define-minor-mode ivy-mode
  "Toggle Ivy mode on or off.
With ARG, turn Ivy mode on if arg is positive, off otherwise.
Turning on Ivy mode will set `completing-read-function' to
`ivy-completing-read'.

Global bindings:
\\{ivy-mode-map}

Minibuffer bindings:
\\{ivy-minibuffer-map}"
  :group 'ivy
